        Returns:

      • rejectDisbursementAndHold

        void rejectDisbursementAndHold()
        Sets the Status to "rejected," and closes down the related, outstanding approval activity, if available. Also creates a TroubleTicket with a Hold on the account to prevent Disbursements from being created or issued. The TroubleTicket is assigned to the ApprovalActivity's assignee, if available. Otherwise, it is autoAssigned.

      • voidDisbursement

        void voidDisbursement()
        Voids this Disbursement by reversing the DisbursementPaid transaction created by this Disbursement, if there is one.
